OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright first thing but
OL,6,Fincreasingly clouding over from the
OL,7,Fwest through the morning with a few
OL,8,Foutbreaks of light rain through the
OL,9,Fafternoon, mainly for Orkney.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy through the evening
OL,12,Fand overnight for Orkney with some
OL,13,Fpatchy light rain, becoming drier
OL,14,Fovernight. Mostly dry for Shetland and
OL,15,Flargely cloudy, though with some
OL,16,Fbreaks at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
