OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FIt will be mainly dry and
OL,6,Fcloudy during the day but with some
OL,7,Fsunny intervals breaking through at
OL,8,Ftimes. Some patchy drizzle possible in
OL,9,Fthe evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fand breezy on Tuesday with some patchy
OL,13,Fdrizzle. Wednesday mainly dry and
OL,14,Fcloudy but with some sunny intervals,
OL,15,Fmost likely for Shetland. Cloudy and
OL,16,Fwindy with light rain Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
